  "description": "<i>Bugs</i> is a shoot 'em up similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/arcade/centipede_\">Centipede</a>. A garden is under attack by various vermins and the player has to use a spray can to defend it. Bugs will appear from the top and move downwards row by row and like in Centipede there are numerous mushrooms that affects their movements. Other creatures include spiders which attack the player from the bottom of the screen, scorpions which lay trails of deadly stings and a snail which move across the screen and leaves a trail that can not be shot through. When all bugs have been killed the game moves on to another level with faster action. ",
